<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>My Technology Guide</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">

  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f4f9ff;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #0066cc;
      margin-top: 25px;
    }

    dl {
      text-align: left;
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 2px solid #0066cc;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    dt {
      color: #0066cc;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    dd {
      margin-left: 20px;
      color: #555;
    }

    hr {
      border-color: #0066cc;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <p class="display-1">TECH WORLD</p>
  <p class="display-2">Amazing Gadgets</p>
  <p class="display-3">Learning Technology</p>
  <p class="display-4">Technology Guide <small>by Jamie</small></p>

  <hr>

  <h2>Popular Devices</h2>

  <dl>
    <dt>Laptop</dt>
    <dd>A portable computer used for study and work.</dd>

    <dt>Tablet</dt>
    <dd>A touchscreen device that is easy to carry.</dd>

    <dt>Smartwatch</dt>
    <dd>A wearable device that shows time and fitness data.</dd>

    <dt>Headphones</dt>
    <dd>Used for listening to music and online classes.</dd>
  </dl>

</body>
</html>
